title: Hearing Someone's Last Breath
itunes:title: Hearing Someone's Last Breath
description:
Ep 124 - In this episode I talk about something that deeply affected me, being present while my grandfather took his last breath. I wanted to be honest and vulnerable and tell you what I learned from being there.
